item.title: Project 2 - Quantum Orchestra
item.description: Qiskit Hackathon Challenge Global for 24 hours Team Memeber Suyeon Park from South Korea, Shek Lun Leung (Alan) from Hong Kong, Rohit Chaurasiya from India, Quentin Sieredzki from the US, and Cynthia Vanessa Rios from the US Mentors: Daniel Sierra-Sosa and James Weaver The exceptional team Description Problem Statement: How can we map quantum states and operations to create music notes with different instruments?
